{"word":"χρονοτριβέω","slug":"χρονοτριβέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χρονοτριβέω</b></el> <el>(χρονο-τρῐβέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τρίβω'><el>τρίβω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to waste time, loiter</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <el>χρ. τὸν πόλεμον</el> <i>to protract</i> the war, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}